title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Zaat
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Zaat
description:
This time on Weirdhouse Cinema, we consider the Florida Movie par excellence: 1971’s “Zaat,” also known as “The Blood Waters of Dr. Z.” Prepare to stalk and skulk through the sargassum in this suitably swampy creature feature.
